!! Writing your own transform

A transform is a tiddler tagged `$:/tags/json-convert/transform`.  Its profile-facing name comes from a `name` field; if absent, the title is slugified (so a tiddler titled ''My Year Bucket'' becomes `my-year-bucket`).  Two body languages are supported, dispatched by the tiddler's `type`.

